<div class="carousel-inner h100">
<a class="carousel-item active">
<div class="fluid-iframe">
<img alt="" class="fluid-element" data-title="樟宜机场网站星期五（6月21日）凌晨突然短暂瘫痪。（档案照片）" src="https://dss1.zbstatic1.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2024/06/21/5B1A0456.JPG?2864951"/>
